snippet.title: SAMURAI SHODOWN NEOGEO COLLECTION - Epic Games Store Launch Trailer
snippet.description: SAMURAI SHODOWN NEOGEO COLLECTION boasts six titles, plus one mysterious and elusive title never-before-seen by the public — and it is now available on the Epic Games Store. Free from June 11 - June 18: http://epic.gm/neogeo
